snippet.title: Beyond The Wire | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Beyond The Wire on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1058650/Beyond_the_Wire/
Sign Up Now for Closed Alpha access: https://signup.playbtw.com/signup

From the muddy flats of no man’s land to the sprawling trench networks, experience WWI like never before with Beyond the Wire.

Join us on discord and be part of the community:
https://discord.playbtw.com

Follow us on social media:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/play_BTW
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/playBTW/
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/beyondthewire/
